OL,3,CHundreds pay their respects to teenage
OL,4,Cboy who died at holiday park
OL,6,FA grieving community has turned out
OL,7,Fonce again to pay their respects at
OL,8,Fthe funeral for a teenage boy who died
OL,9,Falongside his girlfriend at a holiday
OL,10,Fpark.
OL,12,F17-year-old Ethan Slater was found
OL,13,Fdead in a cabin at Little Eden Holiday
OL,14,FPark in Bridlington on 18 February
OL,15,Falongside Cherish Bean, who was 15.
OL,17,FAn inquest at Hull Coroner's Court
OL,18,Fheard their deaths were suspected to
OL,19,Fhave been caused by carbon monoxide
OL,20,Fpoisoning.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
