PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775499063
OL,3,CHundreds pay their respects to teenage
OL,4,Cboy who died at holiday park
OL,6,FLast week thousands of people gathered
OL,7,Fin Parsons Cross for 15-year-old
OL,8,FCherish's funeral and people came out
OL,9,Fin force again on Thursday to remember
OL,10,FEthan.
OL,12,FBlue balloons lined the streets along
OL,13,Fthe funeral procession route from the
OL,14,Ffamily home to St Mary's Church in
OL,15,FEcclesfield.
OL,17,FThe teenager's family had asked the
OL,18,Fcommunity to walk with them on
OL,19,F"Ethan's final journey."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
