PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775499063
OL,3,CHundreds pay their respects to teenage
OL,4,Cboy who died at holiday park
OL,6,FFriends said the 'cheeky, independent
OL,7,Fboy' would be sorely missed.
OL,9,F"He had a heart like no other, he
OL,10,Floved Cherish loads. Him not being
OL,11,Fhere, everyone feels it, it's not just
OL,12,Fone person, everyone here is feeling
OL,13,Fit," said one friend.
OL,15,FAmeera, who grew up with Ethan added,
OL,16,F"I was quite close with them, it's
OL,17,Fhorrible to know what's happened (...)
OL,18,Fit's just hell."
OL,26,@yD@bpmyD@fpn
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
