PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775499063
OL,3,CHundreds pay their respects to teenage
OL,4,Cboy who died at holiday park
OL,6,FVicar, Rev Dr Tim Gill, said he hoped
OL,7,Fthe response would bring some comfort
OL,8,Fto the family.
OL,10,F"I think at the end of last week's
OL,11,Fservice it just hit me that words are
OL,12,Finadequate, there's nothing anyone can
OL,13,Fsay that is going to be of any healing
OL,14,For comfort to the family.
OL,16,F"I don't know how you go about
OL,17,Farranging the funeral of a child as a
OL,18,Fdad or a grandad. The response of the
OL,19,Fcommunity is that realisation that it
OL,20,Fis such a devastating thing to happen
OL,21,Fto a family.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
