FL,367,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1775499063
OL,3,CHundreds pay their respects to teenage
OL,4,Cboy who died at holiday park
OL,6,F"I hope they have comfort in that they
OL,7,Fare thought of and held in the comfort
OL,8,Fof the community."
OL,10,FAn inquest which opened into the
OL,11,Fcouple's deaths heard they had been on
OL,12,Fa family holiday and had both been
OL,13,F"fit and well" when the family spent
OL,14,Fthe evening together on 17 February.
OL,16,FSenior coroner Prof Paul Marks said
OL,17,FCherish and Ethan were staying in a
OL,18,Fsmaller cabin, known as the "man cave"
OL,19,Fwhere they were found dead.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@NO]
